Bring File
Bring Json
Bring Http
Bring Time
Bring OS
Bring Regex
Bring String
Bring List

Keep Data File be "tasks.json"
Keep Remote Endpoint be "https://example.test/tasks"
Keep Title Pattern be "^[A-Za-z0-9 ,._-]+$"

Note A small interactive task board showing the plain-English syntax.
Notes
  It stores tasks as JSON, filters with anonymous teachings,
  syncs with HTTP, uses Result errors, and sends messages to a worker.

Type Task Id means Int
Type Command means Add Command or Done Command or List Command or Search Command or Sync Command or Help Command or Quit Command

Problem App Error
  Has Message Text as String

  Teach Message using Self
    Message Text of Self

Contract Jsonable
  Teach To Json using Self

Record Task
  Has Id as Task Id
  Has Title as String
  Has Done as Bool
  Has Priority as Int
  Has Tags as Set of String
  Has Note as Maybe String
  Has Created At as String

  Teach Label using Self
    Make State be If Done of Self
      "done"
    Otherwise
      "open"
    "#{Id of Self} [{State}] p{Priority of Self} {Title of Self}"

  Teach To Json using Self
    Map with
      "id" meaning Id of Self
      "title" meaning Title of Self
      "done" meaning Done of Self
      "priority" meaning Priority of Self
      "tags" meaning Tags of Self
      "note" meaning Note of Self
      "created_at" meaning Created At of Self

Record Add Command
  Has Title as String
  Has Tags as Set of String

Record Done Command
  Has Id as Task Id

Record List Command
  Has Only Open as Bool

Record Search Command
  Has Query as String

Record Sync Command
  Has Reason as String

Record Help Command
  Has Empty as Bool

Record Quit Command
  Has Empty as Bool

Record Sync Message
  Has Reason as String
  Has Created At as String

Object Secret Settings
  Private Has Token as String

  Teach Redacted using Self
    "hidden"

Object Task Store follows Jsonable
  Has Path as String
  Has Tasks as List of Task
  Has Last Id as Int

  Teach Next Id using Self
    Change Last Id of Self to Last Id of Self plus 1
    Last Id of Self

  Teach Add Task using Self and Title as String and Tags as Set of String and Priority be 1
    If Use Regex Match with Title and Pattern be Title Pattern
      Make Id be Use Next Id of Self
      Make Today be Use Time Format with Use Time Now and "yyyy-mm-dd"
      Make Task be New Task with Id be Id and Title be Title and Done be false and Priority be Priority and Tags be Tags and Note be nothing and Created At be Today
      Use List Add with Tasks of Self and Task
      Success Task
    Otherwise
      Failure New App Error with Message Text be "Task titles may use letters, numbers, spaces, comma, period, underscore, and dash."

  Teach Complete using Self and Id as Task Id
    Repeat for Index in Indices of Tasks of Self
      Make Maybe Task be Item Index of Tasks of Self as Maybe Task
      Match Maybe Task
        When Some Task
          If Id of Task is Id
            Make Updated be New Task with Id be Id of Task and Title be Title of Task and Done be true and Priority be Priority of Task and Tags be Tags of Task and Note be Note of Task and Created At be Created At of Task
            Use List Replace At with Tasks of Self and Index and Updated
            Success Updated
        When nothing
          Skip
    Failure New App Error with Message Text be "No task has id {Id}."

  Teach Open Tasks using Self
    Use List Filter with Tasks of Self and Teach using Task give not Done of Task

  Teach Tagged using Self and Tag as String
    Use List Filter with Tasks of Self and Teach using Task give Tag is in Tags of Task

  Teach Search using Self and Query as String
    Make Lowered be Use String Lower with Query
    Use List Filter with Tasks of Self and Teach using Task give Use String Contains with Use String Lower with Title of Task and Lowered

  Teach Summary using Self
    Make Open Items be Use List Filter with Tasks of Self and Teach using Task give not Done of Task
    Make Done Items be Use List Filter with Tasks of Self and Teach using Task give Done of Task
    Tuple with Length of Open Items and Length of Done Items

  Teach To Json using Self
    Use List Map with Tasks of Self and Teach using Task give Use To Json of Task

  Teach Save using Self
    Make Text Value be Need Use Json Serialize with Use To Json of Self
    Need Use File Write with Path of Self and Text Value
    Success "saved"

Object Remote Task Store extends Task Store
  Has Remote Url as String

  Async Teach Push using Self
    Make Body be Need Use Json Serialize with Use To Json of Self
    Make Response be Need Await Use Http Post with Remote Url of Self and Json be Body
    Need Use Json of Response

Teach Empty Store using Path
  New Task Store with Path be Path and Tasks be Empty List and Last Id be 0

Teach Load Store using Path returns Result of Task Store or App Error
  If Use File Exists with Path
    Make Text Value be Need Use File Read with Path
    Make Rows be Need Use Json Parse with Text Value
    Make Tasks be Empty List
    Make Highest be 0
    Repeat for Row in Rows
      Make Task be New Task with Id be Id of Row and Title be Title of Row and Done be Done of Row and Priority be Priority of Row and Tags be Use Set From with Tags of Row and Note be Note of Row and Created At be Created At of Row
      Use List Add with Tasks and Task
      If Id of Task is greater than Highest
        Change Highest to Id of Task
    Make Loaded be New Task Store with Path be Path and Tasks be Tasks and Last Id be Highest
    Success Loaded
  Otherwise
    Make Empty be Use Empty Store with Path
    Success Empty

Teach Parse Tags using many Words as String
  Make Tags be Empty Set
  Repeat for Word in Words
    Make Clean be Use String Trim with Word
    If Clean is ""
      Skip
    Use Set Add with Tags and Clean
  Tags

Teach Parse Command using Line as String returns Command
  Make Trimmed be Use String Trim with Line
  Make Parts be Use String Split with Trimmed and By be " "
  Match Parts
    When List starting with "add" and many Words
      Make Title be Use String Join with Words and By be " "
      New Add Command with Title be Title and Tags be Set with "inbox"
    When List with "done" and Id Text
      Match Use Int Parse with Id Text
        When Success Id
          New Done Command with Id be Id
        When Failure Error
          New Help Command with Empty be true
    When List with "list"
      New List Command with Only Open be false
    When List with "open"
      New List Command with Only Open be true
    When List starting with "search" and many Words
      New Search Command with Query be Use String Join with Words and By be " "
    When List with "sync"
      New Sync Command with Reason be "manual"
    When List with "help"
      New Help Command with Empty be true
    When List with "quit"
      New Quit Command with Empty be true
    When anything
      New Help Command with Empty be true

Teach Print Help
  Make Help be Text
    Commands:
      add TITLE
      done ID
      list
      open
      search WORDS
      sync
      help
      quit
  Say Help

Teach Print Tasks using Tasks as List of Task
  If Length of Tasks is 0
    Say "No tasks."
  Otherwise
    Repeat for Index and Task in Indexed Tasks
      Make Badge be If Index is less than 9
        " "
      Otherwise
        ""
      Say "{Badge}{Index plus 1}. {Use Label of Task}"
      Match Note of Task
        When Some Note Text
          Say "    note {Note Text}"
        When nothing
          Skip

Teach Print Summary using Store as Task Store
  Make Open Count and Done Count be Use Summary of Store
  Make Pairs be Use List Zip with List with "open" and "done" and List with Open Count and Done Count
  Repeat for Name and Count in Pairs
    Say "{Name}: {Count}"

Teach Priority Report using Store as Task Store
  Make Sorted be Use List Sort with Tasks of Store and By be Teach using Task give Priority of Task
  Make Total be Use List Reduce with Sorted and 0 and Teach using Sum and Task give Sum plus Priority of Task
  Say "Priority total: {Total}"
  Use Print Tasks with Sorted

Teach Tasks Created Today using Store as Task Store
  Make Today be Use Time Format with Use Time Now and "yyyy-mm-dd"
  Use List Filter with Tasks of Store and Teach using Task give Created At of Task is Today

Teach Title Contains using Word as String
  Make Needle be Use String Lower with Word
  Teach using Task give Use String Contains with Use String Lower with Title of Task and Needle

Async Teach Sync Worker using Inbox as Channel of Sync Message and Store as Remote Task Store
  Repeat forever
    Make Maybe Message be Await Receive from Inbox as Maybe Sync Message
    Match Maybe Message
      When Some Message
        Try
          Say "Sync started: {Reason of Message}"
          Make Remote Result be Need Await Use Push of Store
          Say "Sync finished at {Created At of Message}"
        Catch Error
          Say "Sync failed: {Use Message of Error}"
        Finally
          Await Use Time Sleep with Seconds be 1
      When nothing
        Stop

Async Teach Sync Now using Store as Remote Task Store
  Make Response be Need Await Use Push of Store
  Say "Remote accepted {Count of Response} tasks."

Teach Seed Examples using Store as Task Store
  If Length of Tasks of Store is greater than 0
    Success "already seeded"
  Otherwise
    Repeat for Number in Range from 1 to 3
      Make Title be "Example task {Number}"
      Make Task be Need Use Add Task of Store with Title and Tags be Set with "example" and Priority be Number
    Need Use Save of Store
    Success "seeded"

Async Teach Main
  Make Args be Use OS Args
  Make Path be Match Item 0 of Args
    When Some First Arg
      First Arg
    When nothing
      Data File
  Make Store be Need Use Load Store with Path
  Make Remote be New Remote Task Store with Path be Path of Store and Tasks be Tasks of Store and Last Id be Last Id of Store and Remote Url be Remote Endpoint
  Make Inbox be New Channel of Sync Message with Capacity be 10
  Make Worker be Spawn Use Sync Worker with Inbox and Remote
  Make Banner be Text
    twohundredseventyone taskboard
    Type help to see commands.
  Say Banner
  Need Use Seed Examples with Store
  Send New Sync Message with Reason be "startup" and Created At be Use Time Format with Use Time Now and "hh:mm:ss" to Inbox
  Make Running be true
  Repeat while Running
    Make Line be Ask "taskboard"
    Make Command be Use Parse Command with Line
    Match Command
      When Add Command named Add
        Try
          Make Task be Need Use Add Task of Store with Title of Add and Tags be Tags of Add
          Need Use Save of Store
          Say "Added {Use Label of Task}"
        Catch Error
          Say Use Message of Error
      When Done Command named Done
        Try
          Make Task be Need Use Complete of Store with Id of Done
          Need Use Save of Store
          Say "Completed {Title of Task}"
        Catch Error
          Say Use Message of Error
      When List Command named List Request
        If Only Open of List Request
          Use Print Tasks with Use Open Tasks of Store
        Otherwise
          Use Print Tasks with Tasks of Store
        Use Print Summary with Store
      When Search Command named Search
        Make Matches be Use Search of Store with Query of Search
        Use Print Tasks with Matches
      When Sync Command named Sync
        Send New Sync Message with Reason be Reason of Sync and Created At be Use Time Format with Use Time Now and "hh:mm:ss" to Inbox
        Say "Sync queued."
      When Help Command named Help
        Use Print Help
        Use Priority Report with Store
      When Quit Command named Quit
        Say "Goodbye."
        Change Running to false
      When anything
        Say "Unknown command."
  Use Close of Inbox
  Await Worker
  Need Use Save of Store
  Success "done"
